(992, 1, '2017-07-04 00:16:25', '2017-07-04 00:16:25', 'MADE BY STORY &amp; CLARK. SQUARE BEVELED MIRROR\r\nWITH CARVED WOODEN CIRCLE AND GRILL WORK IN FRONT\r\nTWO SMALLER BEVELED EDGED MIRRORS ON EITHER SIDE OF\r\nTOP OF ORGAN. OVER 100 YEARS OLD IN 1970.\r\nHISTORY: THE ORGAN WAS ORIGINALLY OWNED BY WILLIAM VARNEY SR. IRENE WRIGHT\'S GREAT GRANDFATHER. IT HAD BEEN IN THE FAMILY FOR OVER ONE HUNDRED YEARS WHEN IT WAS GIVEN TO THE MUSEUM IN 1970. ONE EVENING AS THE FAMILY WAS SINGING, THE LAMP ON THE LEFT SIDE OF THE ORGAN STARTED THE ORGAN ON FIRE. NOT MUCH DAMAGE ENSUED AS THE FIRE WAS QUICKLY EXTINGUISHED LEAVING ONLY A SMALL CHARRED SPOT ON THE FRONT OF THE ORGAN.\r\nGIVEN BY IRENE WRIGHT THE AMERICAN FORK CITIZEN THURSDAY, FEBRUARY 12, 1970 HAD THIS ARTICLE ALONG WITH A PICTURE OF IRENE V. WRIGHT. “ A BEAUTIFUL ANTIQUE PUMP ORGAN HAS BEEN PRESENTED TO THE A.F. DAUGHTERS OF UTAH PIONEERS MUSEUM BY MRS. IRENE V. WRIGHT. A LOVELY ORNATE PIECE OF FURNITURE, THE 13 STOP STORY AND CLARK ORGAN WAS PURCHSED BRAND NEW BY MRS. WRIGHT\'S GRANDFATHER WILLIAM VARLEY, SR. MR. VARLEY A PROMINENT BUSINESSMAN WAS A WEALTHY QUARRY OWNER DURING HIS COLORFUL LIFETIME. HE PURCHASED THE ORGAN FOR BOTH THE BEAUTY AND THE MUSICAL INSTRUMENT WOULD ADD TO HIS HOME AND FOR THE FINE TONE OF THE INSTRUMENT. MR. VARLEY WAS BORN IN 1837.\r\nA ROUND MIRROR IS CENTERED ON THE ORGAN BACKING WITH MATCHING OBLONG PRISM MIRRORS ON SMALL CUPBOARD SPACES ON EITHER SIDE OF THE GRILLWORK, BEAUTIFULLY CRAFTED OF TURNED WOOD. SMALL WOODEN BALLS AND SPINDELS ARE FEATURED IN THE DECORATIVE RAIL ATOP THE ORGAN, WHICH IS ABOUT SEVEN FIEET HIGH.\r\nTHE ORGAN HAS BEEN IN THE FAMILY FOR OVER 100 YEARS, WITH MRS. WRIGHT\'S FATHER, WILLIAM VARLEY, JR., THE SECOND OWNER. SHE ACQUIRED THE ORGAN FROM FAMILY MEMBERS MANY YEARS AGO AND HAD NEW BELLOWS PUT IN THE INSTRUMENT AND RESTORED IT TO WORKING ORDER.\r\nTHE CAREFULLY CARPETED PEDALS HAVE SEEN MUCH USE OVER THE YEARS, WITH THE ORGAN THE CENTER OF THE MUSICAL ACTIVITIES OF MANY OF THE FAMILY MEMBERS THROUGH THE YEARS.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/wp/item/organ-tall-dark-wood/rsz_atf69/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-993\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-993\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/rsz_atf69-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAF:86:949 CENTER GALLERY FACING EAST PICTURE 69 ATF#69', 'ORGAN (TALL DARK WOOD)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'organ-tall-dark-wood', '', '', '2017-07-04 00:16:25', '2017-07-04 00:16:25', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8080/wp/?post_type=item&#038;p=992', 0, 'item', '', 0),
